schools.name: Jack M Fields Sr Elementary School

data.description: Welcome home just in time for the holidays! Want to downsize or first-time home buyer? Must take a look at this lovely home. It has been taken care of with much love. Smoke free and pet free. Refrigerator, Washer/Dryer and living room tv not included. TV mount will stay. Granite counters, laminate flooring in living, kitchen, dining and wet areas. Carpet in bedrooms. Primary bedroom has a nice size walk-in closet. Primary bath has a great walk-in shower. Room sizes approximate, buyers verify. Make an offer today, seller is motivated!
